reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good fitting filler - Just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: These fillers are just right...Nothing fancy, just foam molded strips that fit neatly between the drivers console and the seat. Perfect. I am very pleased - and pricing was also just right. Replacing a older piece that was more expensive and not as effective.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best thing since sliced bread
reviews.reviewText: Best $10 spent . Fits perfect in a 2012 Honda pilot, got rid of that annoying gap between the seat and the console. Now my phone doesn't disappear in the "black hole". Nice smooth finish and easily installed and easy to remove. Only wish they had a grey color for the same price. Buy these,you won't regret it!

Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Does the job!
reviews.reviewText: I drop EVERYTHING in between my seats. My phone, earrings, chapstick, rings, YOU NAME IT! So for Christmas I ordered myself these and so far so good! It was a little tough to fit in between my seats but I made it work. The description said it fit most seats so hopefully I did it right lol. The black matches right with my seats so it doesn’t stand out and it looks great

Like the headline says... it's very easy to install and super flexible to shove in between the seat. My drivers side did pop up abit but I just shoved it back into the crack and all was fine. The passenger side has not moved since being installed.
I was really looking forward to using these fillers to prevent items slipping in the sides of the seats, however, they were too small for my car. Had to return them. Would be great if they fit.
